{"tid":1559020,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"篤灰熱線其實恐怖過智能燈柱 （一定要推上國際）","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:27:12.000Z","uid":188828,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a218e3a17aa53a834e27274c8ebcedd33da5e7","tid":1559020,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"大家諗下<br />\n你身邊隨時就有個藍絲癲佬篤你灰<br />\n你樓下看更見你發完夢趕住返屋企<br />\n見到你啲文具又可以篤你<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖係 中共式被自殺<br />\n你諗下隔離鄰居樓下看更知你地址<br />\n隨時派黑社會攪9你<br />\n派公安滅你門都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n呢單野一撚定要推上國際<br />\n唔好諗住一個message 唔緊要<br />\n最恐怖係會關乎你人身安全！！！！同家人安全！！！！<br />\n你諗下平時發夢包到咁實就係要隱藏身分<br />\n宜家呢個熱線會暴露身分啊！！！！！！"},{"pid":"c3af1d0355d309543bebdeceed7d7fbc6da9292d","tid":1559020,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:54:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9ff8a0609c53aa38db9c661292c87539013c9ba8","tid":1559020,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1361bb91af61690a64373df85d347edb5567f20","tid":1559020,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8e42d0ee1c3d875b3e57c8f8d4763ac386a659d","tid":1559020,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"196531516b20f291d58a91ddb1ec67c37d30ffc5","tid":1559020,"uid":188828,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"根本係1984 書入面既 秘密警察<br />\n再加上休班警都可以有權用警棍打人<br />\n根本已經係好恐怖既一件事"},{"pid":"50aa1c1c748123bc3351831d4b76a716e66d66c5","tid":1559020,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd795076c1b2c90cbaaf1b45f93070c9fb1dfc8f","tid":1559020,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"諗起v煞班秘密警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p